        <div class="grid">
            <div class="grid-item"><img src="job1.jpg" alt="Roofing"><div class="grid-label">Roofing & Siding</div></div>
            <div class="grid-item"><img src="job2.jpg" alt="Driveway"><div class="grid-label">Driveways & Sidewalks</div></div>
            <div class="grid-item"><img src="job3.jpg" alt="Storefront"><div class="grid-label">Restaurants & Store Fronts</div></div>
            <div class="grid-item"><img src="van.jpg" alt="Windows"><div class="grid-label">Windows & Gutters</div></div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">We also do Graffiti Removal and more!</p>
    </section>

    <section class="reviews">
        <h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
        <div class="review-flex">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Best in OKC! They arrived right on time and did an amazing job on our restaurant storefront. Trust the process!"</p>
                <strong>- Local Business Owner</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Very reasonably priced and the financing option made it so easy to get our whole house and driveway done at once."</p>
                <strong>- Happy Resident</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Professional crew and top-tier equipment. You can really tell they use high-quality chemicals."</p>
                <strong>- David H.</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61563212726715" class="social"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
        <p>Dices LLC | Oklahoma City, OK</p>
        <p>Email: diceswindowllc@gmail.com | Phone: 405-902-7444</p>
        <p>© 2026 Dices LLC. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
